Revision history for MAD-Loader

3.1.0   2014-09-15
            - Added new function 'load_and_new' to functional interface

3.0.0   2013-08-04
            - New attributes
            - New functional interface
            - Changing from Test::More to Test::Most
            - Incompatible with 2.x series

2.0.3   2013-03-02
            - Setting minimum version of Carp as dependency

2.0.2   2013-02-14
            - Fix on some eval/$@ issues
            - Fix on pod typo

2.0.1   2013-02-12
            - Correcting pod typo

2.0.0   2013-02-12
            - Full rewrite of the module.

1.0.0   2013-01-24
            - Adding option on_error
            - Adding option no_import
            - Retrieving initializer return values

0.0.3   2012-09-25
            - Correcting typo

0.0.2   2012-09-11
            - A bit more Kwalitee compliance

0.0.1   2012-08-29
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

